                <h4 data-uuid="bad92ffd700140299fb762ac782b093d">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="e41b8b937d914064a328b20f66ba60c4">The framers of the Constitution devised a federal system that divides power between the national and state governments and creates three separate branches of national government.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="0ccbb98515bd4f7fac4da5c2eb26ef47">The Federal System</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="8fa3a257728240249f27e8892c2943f4"></div>
            </article>
