                <h2 data-uuid="2cf2ef18f3d54574b1f076e0f5425850">Dividing Government Power</h2>
                <p data-uuid="aebbc8747a344c5e8801a0c23f091f22">The Constitution assigns delegated powers to the national government, reserved powers to the states, and concurrent or shared powers to both.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
